      "text": "You won&#39;t be penalized for making too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 204710.0,
      "end_time": 207490.0,
      "text": "Some conservatives like the idea of a universal basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 207490.0,
      "end_time": 208950.0,
      "text": "because it could potentially replace"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 208950.0,
      "end_time": 211119.0,
      "text": "or significantly reduce the current welfare system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 211120.0,
      "end_time": 215430.0,
      "text": "which cost almost $730 billion in 2017."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 215430.0,
      "end_time": 220600.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s almost 20% of the entire federal budget. Wow."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 220600.0,
      "end_time": 222800.0,
      "text": "A universal basic income would make government smaller"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 222800.0,
      "end_time": 224980.0,
      "text": "and it would put the choice of how to spend the money"
