    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 226610.0,
      "end_time": 228920.0,
      "text": "of having the government telling you what to do with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 228920.0,
      "end_time": 231959.0,
      "text": "Now, at this point, we haven&#39;t really talked about cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 231960.0,
      "end_time": 234700.0,
      "text": "Spoiler alert: it&#39;s also really expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 234700.0,
      "end_time": 236959.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a big reason why a lot of people oppose it."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 236960.0,
      "end_time": 238680.0,
      "text": "If the federal government gave every one"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 238680.0,
      "end_time": 241227.0,
      "text": "of the 300 million plus people living in the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 241227.0,
      "end_time": 245570.0,
      "text": "$12,000 a year the total cost would be around $3.8 trillion."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 245570.0,
      "end_time": 247549.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s a hard sell considering"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 247550.0,
      "end_time": 250130.0,
      "text": "the entire federal budget for 2017"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 250130.0,
      "end_time": 252930.0,
      "text": "was a little over four trillion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 252930.0,
      "end_time": 254910.0,
      "text": "To pay for it, one option is for the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 254910.0,
      "end_time": 257329.0,
      "text": "to bring in more money, which means raising taxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 257329.0,
      "end_time": 259909.0,
      "text": "something most conservatives are firmly against."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 259910.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261700.00000000003,
      "text": "Many are also worried that giving people"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 261700.0,
      "end_time": 263920.0,
      "text": "no strings attached free money would discourage them"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 263920.0,
