    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 284240.0,
      "end_time": 285670.0,
      "text": "and have to go to the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 285670.0,
      "end_time": 288610.0,
      "text": "One day alone could cost $5,000 or more."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 288610.0,
      "end_time": 290200.0,
      "text": "That universal basic income money"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 290200.0,
      "end_time": 291770.0,
      "text": "would then run out pretty fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 291770.0,
      "end_time": 293500.0,
      "text": "Now, what&#39;s tricky about evaluating"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 293500.0,
      "end_time": 294700.0,
      "text": "all these different arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 294700.0,
      "end_time": 297599.0,
      "text": "is that we don&#39;t have much real-world data to look at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 297600.0,
      "end_time": 298720.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 298720.0,
      "end_time": 300350.0,
      "text": "There are some experiments out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 300350.0,
      "end_time": 303120.0,
      "text": "Stockton, California is giving $500 a month"
